sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant App as Expo Mobile App
    participant Auth as Firebase Auth
    participant Functions as Callable Functions
    participant Firestore as Cloud Firestore
    participant SQLite as Local SQLite
    participant Files as Local File Storage

    User->>App: Open BabyMinimo
    App->>Auth: Check auth state
    Auth-->>App: Authenticated / unauthenticated

    alt New user
        User->>App: Sign up
        App->>Auth: Create account
        Auth-->>App: User created

        User->>App: Add baby
        App->>Functions: createHousehold()
        Functions->>Firestore: Create household + membership
        Firestore-->>Functions: Household saved
        Functions-->>App: Household ID

        App->>Functions: createBaby()
        Functions->>Firestore: Create baby profile
        Firestore-->>Functions: Baby saved
        Functions-->>App: Baby ID
    end

    User->>App: Log care event
    App->>Functions: createEvent()
    Functions->>Firestore: Save event
    Firestore-->>App: Realtime event update

    App->>Functions: getHandoffSummary()
    Functions->>Firestore: Read latest events + reminders
    Functions-->>App: Handoff summary

    User->>App: Add photo moment
    App->>Files: Save compressed image locally
    App->>SQLite: Save photo moment metadata
    SQLite-->>App: Local moment available

    App->>App: Merge Firestore events + local moments
    App-->>User: Timeline updated

    User->>App: Sign out
    App->>Auth: signOut()
    Auth-->>App: Session cleared
